{"tid":1557829,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港警方宣佈設 10 條反暴力 WhatsApp 報料熱線","createTime":"2019-09-10T09:20:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T09:47:30.000Z","uid":280176,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2368f7a0b32a687c5d3b74fa7fda334575d4fb28","tid":1557829,"uid":280176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T09:20:51.000Z","msg":"香港警方在今天例行記者會中表示，會開設 10 條反暴力 WhatsApp 報料熱線，盼與市民一起止暴制亂。警方表示，有關熱線只用作接收止暴制亂的信息，而市民更不用預約登記，用法跟平日 WhatsApp 相同。<br />\n<br />\n1.熱線只透過WhatsApp接收反暴力情報，包括資料、相片、錄音、錄像等。<br />\n<br />\n2.熱線不適用於一般報案。<br />\n<br />\n3.WhatsApp 熱線共有 10 條線，分別為：5566 9500、5566 9501、5566 9502、5566 9503、5566 9504、5566 9505、5566 9506、5566 9507、5566 9508、5566 9509<br />\n<br />\n4.警方不會透過熱線索取個人資料，也不會向第三方提供報料人電話及資料。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2019/09/10/whatsapp-hk-police/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2019%2F09%2F10%2Fwhatsapp-hk-police%2F&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdD6wvV4D0jUJVCqNn8v1PCJE%3D&h=de48dcc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2019/09/10/whatsapp-hk-police/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>各位熱心人士快啲send啲刀手嘅相俾佢哋啦</strong><br />\n<br />\n721<br />\n831<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"5c04a2c0fdc185f9d827739a02b0f177f0eec824","tid":1557829,"uid":17878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T09:32:55.000Z","msg":"報返濫權狗啲犯罪片段比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"536879d347db9cd89c7673b124b1734462424e41","tid":1557829,"uid":293698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T09:33:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a26e3891e5b1c262e563564e3f987e5173aa9c87","tid":1557829,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T09:41:34.000Z","msg":"舉報藍屍狗"},{"pid":"0044f2c89595190b248fae7ae6a